00:46:23,697 --> 00:46:26,325
Walang dahilan
para pumunta dito, Sarhento Yun.

639
00:46:26,408 --> 00:46:28,869
Kailangan kong maging handa, Mr. Lee.

640
00:46:31,121 --> 00:46:32,039
Aba,

641
00:46:33,165 --> 00:46:34,249
magtiwala sa ginagawa ko.

642
00:46:34,333 --> 00:46:36,084
Kailangan ko pa ring maghanda at maghanda.

643
00:46:56,605 --> 00:46:57,439
TAO TE CHING

644
00:47:00,859 --> 00:47:03,695
LUMUNKIN ITO NG 1 P.M. DALAWANG ARAW MULA NGAYON
ILABAS KO KAYO

645
00:47:52,286 --> 00:47:54,746
Sa huling ito,
mayroon kang walo sa kabuuan.

646
00:47:54,830 --> 00:47:55,747
Dapat maganda.

647
00:47:55,831 --> 00:47:57,499
- Salamat.
- Gun-woo!

648
00:47:57,583 --> 00:47:59,209
- Ikaw sa labas?
- Oo.

649
00:48:01,295 --> 00:48:03,213
Aalis ang team ni Adik ngayon.

650
00:48:03,714 --> 00:48:06,425
Gayunpaman, nawala si Adik.
Nawala na siya.

651
00:48:08,135 --> 00:48:10,554
UZBEK BOXER NAWALA PAGKATAPOS NG TITLE FIGHT.
PULIS NAG-IMBESTIGAHAN.

652
00:48:13,056 --> 00:48:14,224
Masama ang pakiramdam ko, Woo-jin.

653
00:48:14,808 --> 00:48:17,728
I think those assholes are behind this.

654
00:49:04,441 --> 00:49:05,943
Sir, ito po ba ang trabaho?

655
00:49:08,153 --> 00:49:09,154
Kaya lang,

656
00:49:09,655 --> 00:49:11,490
bakit kailangan nating yumuko nang napakababa?

657
00:49:12,783 --> 00:49:14,242
Kami ay sinanay na protektahan.

658
00:49:14,326 --> 00:49:16,411
Paano nakakatulong na sabihin ito ngayon?

659
00:49:17,537 --> 00:49:18,538
Napagkasunduan naming gawin ito.

660
00:49:20,540 --> 00:49:23,168
hindi mo ba naiintindihan
malapit na tayo sa ilalim?

661
00:49:23,669 --> 00:49:25,837
Kailangan din nating bayaran ang ibang mga lalaki.

662
00:49:26,421 --> 00:49:28,465
Hey. Nagtiwala sila sa amin.

663
00:49:29,049 --> 00:49:31,385
Nagsumikap sila at ano ang nakuha nila?
Sirang katawan.

664
00:49:31,468 --> 00:49:33,887
- Oo, alam ko iyon, siyempre, ngunit--
- Jin-nam.

665
00:49:34,972 --> 00:49:37,849
Manatili sa kotse. Kami na ang bahala.

666
00:49:38,558 --> 00:49:42,145
Mr. Jang,
hindi natin matatapos ang trabaho ng dalawa.

667
00:49:43,438 --> 00:49:44,731
Pagbigyan na natin.

668
00:49:58,412 --> 00:49:59,413
Bingo.

669
00:49:59,496 --> 00:50:00,330
HARAP NA PINTO

670
00:50:10,924 --> 00:50:11,967
Oo?

671
00:50:12,551 --> 00:50:13,635
Maaari kang pumasok.

672
00:50:26,273 --> 00:50:27,274
Gawin natin.

673
00:52:01,243 --> 00:52:02,536
Ay, Nanay!

674
00:52:08,500 --> 00:52:10,460
- Gun-woo!
- Kinukuha nila siya.

675
00:52:12,045 --> 00:52:12,879
- Nanay ko!
- Nanay!

676
00:52:12,963 --> 00:52:14,965
- Huwag makipag-away. gagawin ko.
- Trabaho ko ito.

677
00:52:18,802 --> 00:52:21,680
Shit! bastos ka!

678
00:52:48,081 --> 00:52:49,958
- Woo-jin.
- Ano ito?

679
00:52:50,041 --> 00:52:51,835
- Kailangan ko nang umalis.
- Ano?

680
00:52:54,963 --> 00:52:56,089
Gun-woo, okay ka lang?

681
00:54:10,080 --> 00:54:11,998
Ugh!

682
00:54:14,417 --> 00:54:15,418
Kailangan na naming umalis.

683
00:54:17,629 --> 00:54:18,713
Agh!

684
00:55:11,016 --> 00:55:14,894
Shit!

685
00:55:54,893 --> 00:55:56,561
Ay, naku, naku!

686
00:55:59,856 --> 00:56:01,483
Okay ka lang?

687
00:56:01,566 --> 00:56:03,026
- Sobrang sakit!
- Gun-woo!

688
00:56:15,163 --> 00:56:17,248
Tara, alis na tayo. alis na tayo.

689
00:56:20,627 --> 00:56:23,505
Okay ka lang?

690
00:56:23,588 --> 00:56:26,591
- Dito. Kaya mo bang bumangon?
- Hindi, my... Nandiyan ang nanay ko!

691
00:56:31,888 --> 00:56:33,598
Wait lang, nakuha na kita.

692
00:56:39,896 --> 00:56:40,939
Tara, tayo na!

693
00:56:44,567 --> 00:56:45,402
Hoy, tumigil ka!

694
00:56:46,236 --> 00:56:49,364
Bumangon ka na! Tara na! Halika na!

695
00:56:53,910 --> 00:56:56,496
Magmaneho nang mas mabilis! I-floor ito!

